Plot of Number of House Sold

When we look at the number of houses sold plot, it seems there is a fluctuation throughout the years. This shows the data has seasonality. It can be seen an increase on November and December while decrease in the summer season. The Only exception is 2020. There is a highly increasing trend in the summer of 2020. The reason might be the pandemic. From May 2020 to July 2020, the number of house sales increased almost more than 4 times. When it is compared this graph with the house price index and USD currency graphs, we cant see any similarity.
